===Etymology===
Via Middle English and Old French from Latin [[gaudium]]
===Noun===
'''joy''' ([[uncountable]] and [[countable]]; plural: [[joys]])

# The feeling of [[happiness]], [[extreme]] [[cheerfulness]].
#:(''Uncountable''): ''They will be a source of strength and joy in your life''.
# An activity etc which causes this feeling.
#:(''Countable''): ''The Joys and Demands of New Parents''.

